actions.text: Referred to House Committee on Rules.
Reported to House from the Committee on Rules, H. Rept. 94-321.
Measure called up by unanimous consent in House.

official_title: Resolution waiving certain points of order against H.R. 8070, a bill making appropriations for the Department of Housing and Urban Development, and for sundry independent executive agencies, boards, bureaus, commissions, corporations, and offices for the fiscal year ending June 30, 1976, and the period ending September 30, 1976.

summary.text: Waves specified points of order against the bill (H.R. 8070) making appropriations for the Department of Housing and Urban Development, and for sundry independent executive agencies, boards, bureaus, commissions, corporations, and offices for fiscal year 1976, and the period ending September 30, 1976.
